body.p:
In a desktop web browser, the contextual menu of the Edit mode offers
      the following actions:

Undo - this action is available in the contextual menu only after
          you make a change;

Redo - this action is available in the contextual menu only after
          you use the Undo action;

Insert Element - inserts an element at current position;

Rename Element - renames the current element.
